Message.content: This design has top-level non-blocking FIFO/Stream accesses with ap_ctrl_none control interface, which may result in mismatches or simulation hanging.
Aborting co-simulation: C TB simulation failed, nonzero return value '3'.
C TB testing failed, stop generating test vectors. Please check C TB or re-run cosim.

This design has top-level non-blocking FIFO/Stream accesses with ap_ctrl_none control interface which is not supported by cosimulation and could be the cause of this cosimulation failure. Please check the earlier messages to verify that there was indeed a cosimulation mismatch rather than a compilation error. If there was a cosimulation mismatch then verification of this interface combination must be done using a custom RTL testbench. See UG1399 for interface combinations supported by cosimulation.
